description:
TENA Ultra Long Length Liner is specifically designed to manage the thin, fast flow of light bladder leakage. It is our longest liner, with 35% more length than our standard liners, it offers ultimate coverage, security and absorbency. Suitable for anyone who has an active lifestyle.


  • Features TENA Triple Protection against leaks, odour and moisture. 
  • BodyFit™ shape contours to the body for added security.
  • Soft, breathable top sheet for ultimate comfort.
  • Features reseable wrappers, to wrap used liners for discreet and convenient disposal.

Recommended for:


  • Frequent small leaks associated with laughing, coughing and sneezing
  • Leaks when rushing to the toilet
  • Sport and exercise
  • All-day protection for drips and drops
name: Tena Liners Ultra Long 22 Pack
